      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        70.8,
        718.87,
        518.12,
        727.87
      ],
      "text": "Ten aanzien van document 1 wenst UWV nog op te merken dat in dit document is aangegeven dat",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        70.8,
        729.79,
        510.65,
        738.79
      ],
